c: 6
v: 141
t: "Naye niye waloonga emikunda chili nende imisala chilandanga – emilandula- nende echilalandanga, nende mitende nende imimelela chiebiamo bikabukhane, nende imizaituni, nende emikoma chifwanana nende chilafwanana, Lie ebiamo babio olwabibulananga, ne inyanga yokhuchesa murusie eshihanwa shiabio. Ne mulekhonyela khuisasia tawe. Toto ye shiyachama Abandu beyisasia tawe"